## Letter
  ![Letter with crescent seal]("/assets/images/letter.png")
  > The unsealed letter with the broken crescent seal is brief: find the bell beneath the old watchtower before moonrise.

@widget std:item
## Map
  > A charcoal map of Brindlewick and the old road, already soft at the creases.

@widget std:item
## Crate
  > A rain-dark crate from the cloak seller. Bottles clink softly under the lid.

@widget std:item
## DryCloak
  > The dry cloak smells of cedar and sheep oil. It keeps the rain off your back.

@widget std:item
## OldKey
  > The blackened key is cold no matter how long you hold it.

@widget std:item
## Lantern
  > Your lantern burns with a small blue flame that makes every shadow look twice as deep.

@widget std:item
## Chalk
  > The chalk leaves a moon-pale smear on your fingertips.

@widget std:item
## BronzeTongue
  > The bronze tongue is cold and heavy, made for a bell that should not still exist.
